Ticket 3 — PC Running Slow
User: Maria L.
Department: HR
Issue: “My computer takes forever to open apps.”

🔍 Technician Notes
Symptoms consistent with low RAM or high CPU

Possible disk space issue

🧪 Troubleshooting Steps
Ran PC Health Report Tool

Checked CPU Load

Checked Memory Usage

Checked Disk Space

Reviewed startup apps

Verified Windows Update status

📊 Findings
RAM: 7.8 GB used / 8 GB total

Disk: 4 GB free on C:

Windows Update pending restart

✅ Resolution
Cleared 12 GB of temp files

Disabled Teams auto‑start

Restarted system to complete updates

Performance returned to normal.

📌 Preventative Recommendation
Recommend upgrading to 16 GB RAM.
